== 发行 ==
[[百代电影公司|百代]]于2015年10月12日在英国和爱尔兰发行本片<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/oct/07/suffragette-review-votes-women-carey-mulligan-abi-morgan-bonham-carter |title=Suffragette review – a valuable, vital film about how human rights are won |last=Bradshaw |first=Peter |date=2015-10-07 |work=The Guardian |accessdate=2015-10-15 |archive-date=2015-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015205630/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/oct/07/suffragette-review-votes-women-carey-mulligan-abi-morgan-bonham-carter |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年3月27日，[[相对论传媒|相对论传媒]]原本打算只在美国发行电影，由于相对论申请破产，制片方已经把英国放入市场，新的发行方还不得而知。之后[[焦点影业|焦点影业]]于2015年3月17日经相对论从百代手中收购了电影的北美发行权，宣布影片于2015年10月23日在美国有限发行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/03/meryl-streeps-suffragette-gets-fall-release-date-1201400063/ |title=Meryl Streep’s ‘Suffragette’ Gets Fall Release Date |last=Pedersen |first=Erik |date=2015-03-27 |work=Deadline |accessdate=2015-04-06 |archive-date=2015-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150407000406/http://deadline.com/2015/03/meryl-streeps-suffragette-gets-fall-release-date-1201400063/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年6月，电影被宣布为[[伦敦影展|伦敦影展]]开幕影片，于2015年10月7日欧洲首映。伦敦影展主任克莱尔·斯图尔特（{{lang|en|Clare Stewart}}）表示莎拉·加夫隆的故事片是一部“紧迫且令人信服的、由英国妇女制作的、关于改变历史进程的英国妇女的电影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://whatsworthseeing.com/suffragette-to-open-london-film-festival-2015/ |title=What's Worth Seeing: Suffragette to open London Film Festival 2015 |last=Korsner |first=Jason |date=2015-06-03 |work=What’s Worth Seeing… |accessdate=2015-06-03 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304130414/http://whatsworthseeing.com/suffragette-to-open-london-film-festival-2015/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”2015年9月4日，影片在{{le|特柳赖德电影节|Telluride Film Festival}}首映。

{{le|姐妹不删剪|Sisters Uncut}}组织在伦敦首映礼上示威，抗议删掉家庭暴力机构的镜头<ref>{{cite web|author=Keiligh Baker|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3263943/Suffragette-red-carpet-invaded-campaigners-against-domestic-abuse.html|title=Suffragette premiere is invaded by domestic violence campaigners|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-08|work=Daily Mail|archive-date=2015-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008182427/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3263943/Suffragette-red-carpet-invaded-campaigners-against-domestic-abuse.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。海伦娜·博纳姆-卡特称该镜头“完美。如果你有种强烈的感觉，那时你可以把不公正说出来，尝试改变事情。”凯瑞·穆里根表示抗议活动“非常棒”，但她因错过活动而伤心<ref>{{cite web|author=Gander, Kashmira & Townsend, Megan|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/suffragette-premiere-protesters-lie-on-red-carpet-and-let-off-purple-and-green-smoke-in-a6685236.html|title=Suffragette premiere: Protesters lie on red carpet in demonstration against cuts to domestic violence services|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-08|work=The Independent|archive-date=2015-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009034258/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/suffragette-premiere-protesters-lie-on-red-carpet-and-let-off-purple-and-green-smoke-in-a6685236.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

